          "bbox": [
            31.19,
            107.27,
            564.11,
            148.96
          ],
          "text": "Subjective Observations: Patient reports stable blood sugar levels and controlled peripheral neuropathy symptoms with current\nmedication regimen. Reports following a diabetic-friendly diet and mild exercise routine. Denies any recent episodes of\nhypoglycemia or hyperglycemia. Complains of occasional tingling in feet.",
          "char_count": 318
        },
        {
          "bbox": [
            31.19,
            155.46,
            564.11,
            182.98
          ],
          "text": "Assesment: Patient presents with well-managed Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus and stable Peripheral Neuropathy. Lipid profile and renal\nfunction are within acceptable ranges. ECG shows no significant abnormalities.",
          "char_count": 207
        },
        {
          "bbox": [
            31.19,
            189.48,
            564.1,
            216.99
          ],
          "text": "Recommendations: Continue current medication regimen. Reinforce adherence to diabetic diet and exercise plan. Consider adjusting\nGabapentin dosage if tingling becomes bothersome. Consider physical therapy consultation for neuropathy.",
          "char_count": 233
        },
        {
          "bbox": [
            31.19,
            223.49,
            564.1,
            251.01
          ],
          "text": "Follow Up Instruction: Schedule follow-up appointment in 3 months for HbA1c and CMP monitoring. Return sooner if any new\nsymptoms arise or existing symptoms worsen.",
          "char_count": 164
        },
        {
